    "body": "> I was able to replicate this earlier too; what's the plan here, upgrade beacon nodes first?\r\n\r\nYeah. In the release notes for v2.1.0 and v2.1.1 we signalled an intention for the v2.1.x validator _not_ to be compatible with the v2.0.1 BN, so the recommended upgrade path remains the same: upgrade the BNs, and then the VCs shortly after (or in the same update). This panic is just an unsightly error rather than a clean failure.",
